{"tid":2354132,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［開定］2021警察招募討論區","createTime":"2021-01-05T08:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T18:50:55.000Z","uid":311309,"like":12,"dislike":148,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e3b8abe9ad82eb65ddb71618dd70d09ffff409","tid":2354132,"uid":311309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"警員薪酬：警務人員薪級表第3點 (每月23,070元) 至警務人員薪級表第15點 (每月32,985元) (註 2) <br />\n<br />\n督察薪酬：警務人員薪級表第23點 (每月40,825元) (視乎學歷而定) 至警務人員薪級表第42點 (每月80,965元) (註 2)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPC 遴選程序 <br />\n<br />\n1. 初步審核 Initial Screening (IS) <br />\n2. 體能測試 Physical Test (PT) <br />\n3. 小組面試 Group Interview (GI) (唔係叫First In) <br />\n4. 最後面試 Final Interview Board (FIB)(唔係叫Second In) <br />\n5. 品格審查 Vetting <br />\n6. 體格檢驗 Medical Examination (ME)(唔係叫BC) <br />\n7. 警隊覆核委員會 Force Review Board (FRB) <br />\n<br />\n1.IS:核對學歷, 度高, 磅重, 測視力 <br />\n<br />\n度高/磅重:男:最 少 1.63 米 及 體 重 50 公 斤 <br />\n女:最 少 1.52 米 及 體 重 42 公 斤 <br />\n<br />\n可 配 戴 眼 鏡 ， 但 必 須 通 過 視 力 測 試 <br />\n<br />\n2.PT:立地向上跳, 引體上升,一百米來回跑(10x10) <br />\n[計分方法請參考本版最底的體能續分表] <br />\n[300分滿分150分合格] <br />\n<br />\n立地向上跳:男 性 :53.3 厘 米 <br />\n女 性 :38.1 厘 米 <br />\n<br />\n引體上升:男 性 : 7 <br />\n女 性 : 9(腳爭貼地) <br />\n<br />\n一百米(10x10):男 性 :24.8 秒 <br />\n女 性 :28.1 秒 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.GI:4-12個應徵者的小組討論[開波每人1-2分鍾自我介紹] <br />\n<br />\n收Pol.850返屋企填 <br />\n<br />\n4.FIB:自我介紹再問問題等[178必背,5大處,學堂15單元] <br />\n<br />\n5.Vetting:四大範疇[家庭及個人,在學,在職,財務狀&amp;#20917;] <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://6.ME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F6.ME&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=9bc849ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">6.ME</a>:驗身[色弱,色差,弱聽,]要小心,吸煙者最好ME前兩個月戒定 <br />\n<br />\n7.FRB:每個人以上所有關都會有個分send去評[汱弱留強,等得越耐越危險] <br />\n<br />\n急救/拯溺/車牌有分加"},{"pid":"ced430e6880ed189984c5a81fcd79ab963e2669a","tid":2354132,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373facc92942580a4f1e19140ea3d4573889efaf","tid":2354132,"uid":53601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:42:33.000Z","msg":"你啱，做狗都係體育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a52bf3fdd4e418e64fe4c1985791a39e4003d83","tid":2354132,"uid":159653,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:42:39.000Z","msg":"樓主係警察，證據確鑿，我將會開post指證你條五毛狗！"},{"pid":"db5e33bf963a0a7d9664c18e4b011ac1f0ddffce","tid":2354132,"uid":311626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:43:22.000Z","msg":"有冇車牌都考得？"},{"pid":"c9a2104fb04f5ecabb78eff3a5b92597cbb25b84","tid":2354132,"uid":311626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:43:35.000Z","msg":"樓主件衫咩色"},{"pid":"ecf8b007379ee2e8c5e13bb6d31804487d473a40","tid":2354132,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:44:03.000Z","msg":"開海關入境啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26caf9e0d6b13690337c088eb37883456b85af4","tid":2354132,"uid":311309,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"有無手足想實踐抱負？"},{"pid":"23a61993fe92e85f3574f39ad1571b515de9ba4d","tid":2354132,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:46:14.000Z","msg":"我1米62<br />\n博唔博得過"},{"pid":"2d89596224a6271fcef606f264767bdf8dcbc7af","tid":2354132,"uid":311309,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"373facc92942580a4f1e19140ea3d4573889efaf","tid":2354132,"uid":53601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:42:33.000Z","msg":"你啱，做狗都係體育<img src=\"/assets/faces/n